                    <span>Anyone who has read his first book will definitely want to read this one as well.  This book actually helps the reader to implement the Four Agreements into daily life.  Very insightful and I wish I had read it forty years ago!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Beautiful and Practical Guide to Personal Freedom</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>9</span>
                      /
