                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2003-01-03</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>What I most like about all of don Miguel's books is that they are written simply and from the heart. What I most like about this book is that it focuses the reader's attention on observing and releasing non-serving agreements. The techniques are clear, simple and dramatic. I use this book in classes that I teach on the Four Agreements and these tools are very powerful.<p>When we learn to love ourselves and live from our authentic selves, our actions toward others are naturally loving and respectful. This is because our authentic self is love. Don Miguel writes about releasing the illusions of non-serving beliefs which have nothing to do with the truth of who we are in this moment. This frees us up to enjoy our lives and offers great creative power. Give yourself the gift of this book and allow yourself to experience how great life can be.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Grounding Clarity, Simple Truth</div>
